data.description: Live a Country Club lifestyle in the desirable Banning Lewis Ranch neighborhood. This stunning ranch home features luxury hardwood floor, open concept craftmanship flows from the entry through the living room with gas fireplace, passes natural stone kitchen island for informal dining and the  beautiful countertops the wraps around the gourmet kitchen equipped with gas range and modern appliances, and to the dining area filled with natural lights with a walk out to a large patio. This gorgeous ranch has master retreat in the main level with adjoining 5-piece master bath amenities, the 2nd bedroom on the same level can easily convert to an office. The the huge finished basement  awaits a fun family nights or watching games with friends. Entertain them around the wet bar or simply cuddle and enjoy and feel the warmth of the natural gas fireplace. Front and back yard has low- maintenance landscaped with enormous amount of natural flagstones and plenty of raised bed and wood-box gardening.  The covered patio is always  perfect for hosting barbeque party or any gatherings. This property is close to the neighborhoods, parks, club house and just a stone throw from Banning Lewis Ranch Academy. Don't miss out on what this community offers other than great living condition. This community amenities are recreation area, Olympic size lap and family swimming pool with water slides, splash zone, a fitness center with modern equipment and free weight, a group Zumba and Yoga sessions, a Pickle-ball courts, parka, endless hiking trails, a dog parks and organized events such as food trucks, fireworks, concerts, etc. Take a chance to live in the place where harmony and modern living meet and make this as your next home sweet home!
